{"tid":1960974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"因武漢肺炎而失業/home office嘅你，日常生活有咩改變？","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T13:09:15.000Z","uid":60535,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6302fb51ae154e1c91d2217ce4c398f08fc2603","tid":1960974,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<br />\n小弟係自己辭職嘅，因為老細仆街，然後呢段時間成個生活習慣有好多唔同晒。<br />\n<br />\n開始冇打機，原因除咗玩到悶之外，同埋開始冇呢種執著，What happens in Game , stays in Game.<br />\n<br />\n開始自己寫下日記，或者作短故，唔係《林鄭月娥嬌嗔一聲倒在習近平嘅懷裡 》呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n中學時期放下咗嘅嘢嚟畫畫，而家又拎返起。<br />\n<br />\n以前買落有一打小說，而家慢慢睇返。<br />\n<br />\n係咁瞓覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無聊得滯戒丁。<br />\n<br />\n重有少少，不過私人嘢嚟"},{"pid":"083c63e3b12292663efe318a36a51db142c39323","tid":1960974,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"放心啦<br />\n<br />\n樓主你呢種生活可以維持到退休"}]}